+ * Stage 12 fairness tracepoints (conceptual).
+ *
+ * These tracepoints are conceptual and not wired into any build target.
+ * They document the ideal tracepoint set for fairness accounting.
+ *
+ * Event: kairo_fairness_decision
+ *   Emitted when fairness policy makes a throttle/demote decision.
+ *
+ * Event: kairo_fairness_credit_refill
+ *   Emitted when entity credits are refilled.
+ *
+ * CONCEPTUAL-HOOK: These tracepoints depend on the final fairness policy
+ * implementation and should be added to patch 0017 or 0020 after
+ * validation.
+ */
+
+/*
+ * TRACE_EVENT(kairo_fairness_decision,
+ *	TP_PROTO(unsigned int dev, u32 session_id, u32 model_id,
+ *		 u64 service_credit, u64 decode_dispatches,
+ *		 const char *decision),
